high_descs: Turn right and go to the circular coffee table ahead.
Pick up the fork from the table.
Turn around and approach the fridge in the corner to the left.
Open the fridge and place the fork on the plate in the fridge.
Pick up the plate you just put the fork on.
Return to the coffee table you got the fork from.
Put the plate down on the table.

Turn around and go back to the coffee table to your right.
Put the plate with the fork on the coffee table.
